
  SIZE2ANGLE  convert proper to angular size in different cosmologies

  Usage:
	size2angle z=z [Omega=Om Lambda=Ol H0=h0 size=size out=arcmin,deg,rad]

		defaults: Omega=1, Lambda=0, H0=50, size=1kpc, out=arcsec

		you can use units in the size parameter:
			angle=0.3cm
			angle=1kpc
			angle=0.01pc
			angle=1Mpc
		default size units are kpc.


